    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and represents a practical choice for anyone needing a dependable daily driver. Mechanically, it remains solid; the engine starts reliably and the car handles safely on the road. However, the exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, minor paint fading, and a few small dings. The interior also shows signs of regular use, including some wear on the upholstery and minor staining on the carpets. It is a functional, honest car that has served its previous owners well and still has plenty of life left for a budget-conscious buyer.",
