    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I am absolutely thrilled to list this total gem. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape it still feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's been meticulously cared for, garage-kept, and is looking for a new home where it'll be just as loved. If you're looking for something that's practically perfect inside and out, you\u2019ve found it! I\u2019m happy to chat and answer any questions you have\u2014come take a look and see for yourself! \u2728",
      "price": 43500.0,
