      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presented in museum-grade condition, this performance icon features a meticulously maintained naturally aspirated engine with a linear power band and exceptional throttle response. The powertrain is mated to a close-ratio manual gearbox and a limited-slip differential, providing surgical precision during cornering. The undercarriage is pristine, showing no signs of thermal cycling stress or oxidation. The suspension utilizes a sophisticated multi-link setup with all original geometry preserved, ensuring zero deflection. Every fluid analysis and compression test confirms the internal components are operating at factory-new specifications. A true turn-key investment for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 49250.0,
