      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional find: a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously garaged and climate-controlled, evidenced by its flawless, mirror-like exterior finish and complete absence of road rash or door dings. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition; the premium leather upholstery is supple with no creasing, and the 'new car' scent persists. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver-assist features, functions perfectly. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, boasting a documented history of preventative maintenance performed exclusively by certified technicians. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-grade example for the discerning driver who refuses to compromise on quality.",
